:: _Changelog:

v0.2
====

Implement a class IndentityClient with the following methods:

* list_users
* create_user
* get_user_details
* modify_user
* activate_user
* deactivate_user
* renew_user_token

v0.3
====
Implement a simple and minimal REST API
Map VOs to Synnefo projects
Cache user information in an LDAP directory
Authenticate VOMS
Create verified VOMS as Synnefo users, if they don't exist
Renew Synnefo user tokens
Augment response with Synnefo credentials (uuid, token,
project id)
Provide a deployment guide w.r.t. scalability and security

v0.4
====
Introduce two openstack-keystone endpoints, /v2.0/tokens and /v2.0/tenants
Implement POST /v2.0/tokens and GET /v2.0/tenants
Merge Synnefo and EGI information in authentication responses
Remove /authenticate endpoint and corresponding functionality
Minor bugfixes
